% ====================================================================
% SECTION 50: difference -- elements in arr1 not in arr2
% ====================================================================

% basic
[1 2 3 4 5] [3 4 5 6] difference
[1 2] deep-eq                                  (difference: basic) rt-ok clear

% no overlap
[1 2 3] [4 5 6] difference
[1 2 3] deep-eq                                (difference: no overlap) rt-ok clear

% complete overlap
